t objectively though for those encountering this line often.} 5. Bg5 Nbd7 6. dxc6 bxc6 {Transposes to the immediate dxc6 and then Bg5 variation in this chapter--doing Bg5 before taking doesn't change anything over taking and playing Bg5 .} *

