1. e4 d6 2. d4 Nf6 3. Nc3 e5 4. d5 Nbd7 {This will transpose to the Club Player Mainline and I want to cover it there instead of here--merely listing it here in case you thought of it as a deviation and navigated to this chapter.  Click here for a link to that chapter's informational on this position.} *

