1. e4 d6 {Welcome to the user-requested lines! These lines were created post publication and are listed as alternative lines to memorize based on user requests. A few notes and disclaimers before you get to it:  1. There is no video here because this was post publication. I consider the course a complete course without these lines, but these lines enhance the course in addressing tricky and somewhat rare sidelines White has.   2. These lines and the puzzles chapter are not beta tested, being written post publication. So as the New York Subway signs will advise you: 'If you see something, say something.'   I hope you enjoy these additions to the course, optional to memorize.} *

